(1, '<h1><strong>Vaccine Clinic of Vaccine Kart</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vaccine Clinic is an initiative from Vaccine Kart for the people who wanted to get vaccinated at a reliable place with the right type of vaccines which is stored as per the WHO&nbsp;standards. Vaccine Kart had associated with various clinics in and around Kozhikode to cater the needs of the people.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><em>Booster doses of childhood vaccines to refresh the immune system&rsquo;s memory. For e.g. the tetanus injection needs to be given every 10 years of one&rsquo;s adult life.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Mandatory: Students going abroad for studies and some specific yellow fever vaccines were mandatory as part of the visa application process. Likewise for those travelling to Middle East for Haj also need to complete some vaccinations as per Saudi Arabia Government visiting pilgrims&rsquo; norms.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Vaccination related to travel to specific regions or before engaging in specific kinds of activities. For example, those headed for treks in specific countries or likely to be exposed to certain infection due to travel.</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Adult vaccines to prevent from specific diseases or conditions. For instance lifestyles and underlying medical conditions like heart diseases or diabetes in adults, warrant extra protection from infectious disease through vaccinations.</em></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vaccine Counselling Centre:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vaccine counselling is set up to give the people more awareness about the need for vaccination and escapes from most of the dreadful diseases. Understand the necessary of vaccination, the side effects of certain vaccination and more important the stage when one should get vaccinated. &nbsp;Our counsellors work all&nbsp;working days between&nbsp;9.00 am &ndash; 6.00 pm except on Sundays and public holidays.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vaccine Kart is a single point contact for all types of vaccination.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Call us: 62828 02 994 or 0495 2300124</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Contact persons: Raman.N.V. 6382 832 035 / Guruswamy 9656 1111 54</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"marker\"><strong>Vaccine Clinic Associate :</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"marker\"><strong>Doctor&#39;s Polyclinic Chalappuram (0495 2305411)</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h1><span class=\"marker\"><strong>Dr.P.M.Kutty &amp; Dr.Iyad.M.P</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"marker\"><strong>Tuesday : 9.00 AM - 6.00 PM &amp; Saturday 9.00 AM - 6.00 PM</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span class=\"marker\"><em>All appointments for vaccination &amp; vaccine counselling based on prior booking only, over phone.</em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n');

